# SPARC CODEOWNERS — required reviewers per path.
#
# Catch-all uses the broader `sparc-dev` team so day-to-day code review
# is not a single-person bottleneck. Sensitive paths (CI workflows, DB
# migrations, boot-time hooks, compliance artifacts, base image) require
# `sparc-admin` review because changes there affect deploy posture,
# attack surface, or audit obligations.
#
# Last reviewed: 2026-05-24 (#545, pre-public-flip hardening)

# ─── Catch-all ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                               @risk-sentinel/sparc-dev

# ─── CI / Actions ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Workflow changes can introduce secret exfiltration, CI minute drain,
# or fork-PR escalation paths. Admin review required.
/.github/                       @risk-sentinel/sparc-admin
/.github/CODEOWNERS             @risk-sentinel/sparc-admin

# ─── Database migrations ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Schema changes are irreversible in prod without downtime. Admin review
# catches missing indexes, accidental destructive operations, and
# missing idempotent guards (see #537 incident).
/db/migrate/                    @risk-sentinel/sparc-admin

# ─── Boot-time configuration ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Initializers run before Zeitwerk indexes app/ — easy to introduce
# autoload-order bugs that only manifest in container builds.
/config/initializers/           @risk-sentinel/sparc-admin
/config/environments/           @risk-sentinel/sparc-admin

# ─── Compliance artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# OSCAL CDEFs and the NIST 800-53 mapping carry audit weight. Admin
# review keeps the compliance posture coherent across PRs.
/docs/compliance/               @risk-sentinel/sparc-admin

# ─── Base image ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Base image changes affect every deployed instance and shift CVE
# baseline.
/Dockerfile                     @risk-sentinel/sparc-admin
/docker-compose-prod.yaml       @risk-sentinel/sparc-admin
